Title: Antiferromagnetic S=1/2 Heisenberg Chain and the Two-flavor Massless

Schwinger ModelAuthors: Yutaka Hosotani

Comments: 3 pages. LaTex2e

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. B60 (1999) 6198-6199

An antiferromagnetic S=1/2 Heisenberg chain is mapped to the two-flavormassless Schwinger model at \theta=\pi. The electromagnetic coupling constantand velocity of light in the Schwinger model are determined in terms of theHeisenberg coupling and lattice spacing in the spin chain system.